
# TGBT25B_603_12

Test data from TGBT25B_603_12

## Files

Example of data with multiple FITS and flag files and non-overlapping flag rules.
These data can be used to test that union of flag rules works correctly.

Directories:

   * TGBT25B_603_12 : contains the raw SDFITS data and its associated index and flag files.  To save disk space, only contains 3 of 6 files of the whole data set are included (D,F,G). The entire data set would have been 700MB.
